date":"November 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Wahb reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIt is enough sin for a man to get angry when he is told to fear Allah.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 8588 Grade: Rijal al-Sahih (narrators are reliable) according to Al-Haythami \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0628\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36965,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/22\/best-provision-taqwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":32729,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Taqwa: Best provision for travel is fear of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I intend to travel, so supplicate for my provision.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cMay Allah provide you with fear of Him.\u201d The man said, \u201cGive me more.\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33226,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/18\/allah-loves-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":32729,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Allah loves family ties, hates separation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah reported: A man of Khath\u2019am came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, asaying, \u201cAre you the one who considers himself the Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes.\u201d The man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deeds are most beloved to Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34843,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/hadith-khtubah-al-hajah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32729,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Khutbah al-Hajah: How the Prophet began his sermons","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave us the combination of all good things and their endings, for he taught us the statements of prayer and the statements of need. The statements of prayer are, \u201cAll greetings, prayers, and good things are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37275,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/31\/shirk-hope-fear\/","url_meta":{"origin":32729,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Idolatry, losing hope, not fearing Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cWhat are the major sins?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo associate partners with Allah, to despair of relief from Allah, and to feel safe from the plan of Allah. These are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1972,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/17\/akhlaq-fear-allah-wherever\/","url_meta":{"origin":32729,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Fear Allah everywhere, have good character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFear\u00a0Allah wherever you are, follow a bad deed with a good deed and it will erase it, and behave with good character towards people.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1987 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32729","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embed